+# PR_26177_BRAVO_008-delete-empty-tts-profile-parents
+
+## Branch Validation
+- PASS: Initial branch was `bravo/26177-text-to-speech`.
+- PASS: Work stayed on the active Bravo branch; main was not checked out.
